    dc:title "Morphology-based cladistics splinters the century-old dichotomy of the pied harvestmen (Arachnida: Gonyleptoidea: Cosmetidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959536>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959576>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959594>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959580>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959584>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959532>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959620>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959598>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959586> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959536>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Strict consensus of trees obtained with K = 6.2878 and 7.4809, indicating larger groups as defined herein, with asserted distributions juxtaposed. * indicates type species of the genera.Abbreviations: BY = Bayesian analyses, EW = equal weighting, IW = implied weighting, RBS = relative Bremer support, BT = bootstrap, GC = difference in frequencies GC (Group present/Contradicted), PP = posterior probabilities of clades." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959536/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959576>
    dc:description "Figure 24. Kayania bicolumnata, male holotype (SMF 12782/16). A, dorsal view. B, ventral view. C, distal part of the penis emerging through genital operculum. D, habitus, lateral view. E, postero-lateral view. F, original labels by Weyrauch and Roewer. Scale bars: 1 mm. Photos courtesy Abel Pérez." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959576/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959594>
    dc:description "Figure 31. Protus bolivari, male (USNMENT 01538074). A, dorsal view. B, lateral view. C, frontal view. D, panoramic dorsal view. E, ventral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A–C, E), 2 mm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959594/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959580>
    dc:description "Figure 25. Kayania compressicoxa, schematic female illustration modified from Avram & Soares (1983). A, dorsal view. B, ovipositor and detail of macrosetae. C, left chelicera, mesal view. D, right pedipalpus, mesal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959580/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959584>
    dc:description "Figure 27. Marronia elegans, male holotype (SMF RII 8681/13). A, dorsal view. B, panoramic dorsal view. C, original label. Photos courtesy Abel Pérez." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959584/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959532>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Examples of some characters defined by us and used in the present phylogenetic analysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959532/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959620>
    dc:description "Figure 42. Sibambea cincta, male (MPUJ_ENT 644772). A, dorsal view. B, panoramic dorsal view. C, lateral view. D, posterior view. E, ventral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959620/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6959598>
    dc:description "Figure 33. Protus distinctus, male (CAS AK 105).A, dorsal view. B, lateral view. C, panoramic dorsal view.Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6959598/files/figure.png" ;
